gdsc.hometext: Google Developer Student Club (GDSC)  --Mohan Babu University

gdsc.hometitle: Have you completed the Hacktoberfest challenge?⏱️ The clock is ticking — 11 more days to contribute!
gdsc.hometext: Did you know that you can make open source and the environment better by participating in Hacktoberfest? The first 50k participants to complete just 1 accepted pull/merge request will get a tree planted in their name from Tree-Nation.
